wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我同你都係差唔多<br />\n話說上個禮拜同佢一齊去以前既學校拎野<br />\n食午飯果陣講講下先知佢前排拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明之前都仲好地地仲一齊睇奇異博士同埋你的名字<br />\n我10月生日佢都有同我打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n果日之後我冇同佢講過野 佢FB搵我我都冇覆佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3856f12911fcd4a1be01039f5d1e1683c4ca73be","tid":24942,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T23:25:25.000Z","msg":"死心啦 唔好再同自己過唔去"},{"pid":"279ff5eef2bf2f2e26849db231e30aab1891b9db","tid":24942,"uid":52047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:12:30.000Z","msg":"睇到佢開post<br />\n意為佢出左事<br />\n於是即刻打比佢<br />\n原來只係自己傻仔諗多左<br />\n明明就同自己講過唔再搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a13af2a6e2092de4086bfcb56e7feec1c02e574","tid":24942,"uid":40695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同自己講好左唔再諗你㗎啦<br />\n同自己講好左我會小啲諗起你㗎<br />\n我有試過 真係試過<br />\n但係到左深夜 無啦啦又犯賤手痕㩒入你ig到睇<br />\n睇到啦 個心好痛 好掛住你 然後無啦啦又喊<br />\n好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想你搵我 但係又好想唔再諗你<br />\n但其實原來我好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我發洩下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n給我一個理由忘記～<br />\n那麼愛我的你～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7196b2164ad5cb5cc0acad6d7046dc9c299609","tid":24942,"uid":35536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:41:54.000Z","msg":"明白醒覺有定時"},{"pid":"d20b96898b60919ca4b00d85ca599e5459a73b46","tid":24942,"uid":20597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"分左手兩個星期 因為你有第二個<br />\n我鐘意左你8年 同你一齊4年了 <br />\n我個心已經容不下其他人，我會等你<br />\n好掛住你啊"},{"pid":"fd5087a2492ddb58af57ff0f85ae87f1b4cc6081","tid":24942,"uid":5500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"巴打保重<br />\n如果對方已經對你死咗心<br />\n你就無謂再咁上心啦<br />\n唔需要逃避自己對佢嘅感覺<br />\n但都無謂再花心機時間喺佢身上<br />\n過一排可能會有新嘅諗法呢<br />\n共勉之<br />\n利申：啱啱同女朋友鬧分手 冷靜中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a330be31bf80e32bbe0ab86f19b4411fa607ae5","tid":24942,"uid":51775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩都好 唔好再自己屈係個低谷度<br />\n搵多d人傾下呻下<br />\n做多d平時唔會做既野<br />\nget well soon</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我平時係人面前無咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會開心到<br />\n但係一到自己一個人嘅時候就會好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係咁<br />\n跟住班fd 就會話明明就無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12dadcf0b33a331ff4fef9bc78b7faf22309c4b","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩個禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同自己講好左唔再諗你㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n同自己講好左我會小啲諗起你㗎<br />\n<br />\n我有試過 真係試過<br />\n<br />\n但係到左深夜 無啦啦又犯賤手痕㩒入你ig到睇<br />\n<br />\n睇到啦 個心好痛 好掛住你 然後無啦啦又喊<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想你搵我 但係又好想唔再諗你<br />\n<br />\n但其實原來我好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我發洩下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算你幾再傷心佢都唔會知<br />\n<br />\n何必為左一個已經同你無關係既人傷心<br />\n<br />\n封曬同佢有關既野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔捨得block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會祝佢盡快有新歡  等你可以死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實佢而加應該係有個可發展緊嘅對象同佢發展緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知道㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我先要同自己講要諗少啲<br />\n<br />\n而我地成兩個禮拜無傾過計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔敢再搵佢<br />\n<br />\n我開始死緊心㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係仲好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我同你都係差唔多<br />\n話說上個禮拜同佢一齊去以前既學校拎野<br />\n食午飯果陣講講下先知佢前排拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明之前都仲好地地仲一齊睇奇異博士同埋你的名字<br />\n我10月生日佢都有同我打邊爐<br />\n<br />\n果日之後我冇同佢講過野 佢FB搵我我都冇覆佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最怕係好似好地地但係原來佢已經拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229407f22a48058c9cc1fdd9b3256d20f38f73a6","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死心啦 唔好再同自己過唔去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死緊㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要啲時間"},{"pid":"99a5778e0e80b2c90bd78759deef4d20c74c9880","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩個禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同自己講好左唔再諗你㗎啦<br />\n同自己講好左我會小啲諗起你㗎<br />\n我有試過 真係試過<br />\n但係到左深夜 無啦啦又犯賤手痕㩒入你ig到睇<br />\n睇到啦 個心好痛 好掛住你 然後無啦啦又喊<br />\n好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想你搵我 但係又好想唔再諗你<br />\n但其實原來我好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我發洩下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n給我一個理由忘記～<br />\n那麼愛我的你～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n給我一個理由放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d0f0c3ef990a9812faee95f5671bf76dbf7b67","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明白醒覺有定時</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不可以沉下去總可以迷下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54e427c328db9287622b790f8b8a2398ce1858f","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手兩個星期 因為你有第二個<br />\n我鐘意左你8年 同你一齊4年了 <br />\n我個心已經容不下其他人，我會等你<br />\n好掛住你啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你一定好鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b23b0288b4c370722911fd306793b16c8e2aaaa","tid":24942,"uid":10795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"睇topic以為巴打爆肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ad7fe305003eebc4a61d77ff48949cb678aa2d","tid":24942,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打保重<br />\n如果對方已經對你死咗心<br />\n你就無謂再咁上心啦<br />\n唔需要逃避自己對佢嘅感覺<br />\n但都無謂再花心機時間喺佢身上<br />\n過一排可能會有新嘅諗法呢<br />\n共勉之